---
title: Lemon Pepper Chicken Schnitzels with Caramelised Onion Sauce & Radish-Apple Slaw
description: We’re putting a pep in this chicken schnitzel’s step by adding some lemon and pepper seasoning to the golden panko crumb. it will zap through the crunch and blend with the caramelised onion sauce that’s on top of these bad boys. You’ll be skipping to the dinner table in anticipation.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
